# CHAPTER XII<span id="page_15_fr_1"></span>[<sup><span class="small">1</span></sup>](#page_15_note_1.md).

OF THE CREATION OF BEASTS AND ANIMALS.

   O<span class="small">N</span> Friday eve God created them<span
id="page_15_fr_2"></span>[<sup><span
class="small">2</span></sup>](#page_15_note_2.md), and therefore animals
can see at night as well as in the day time. Others say that they were
all created in the morning, and that God created Adam after them on the
sixth day, which is Friday.

